Greenko Group Wins Concessions for Wind, Hydroelectric Projects in India

-- B y   T o d d   W h i t e
-- 
2011-04-14T06:40:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-14/greenko-group-wins-concessions-for-wind-hydroelectric-projects-in-india.html
Greenko Group Plc (GKO)  , a U.K.
developer of clean-energy plants in  India , said it won
concessions to build a 300-megawatt wind-energy plant and
several hydroelectric assets that total 50 megawatts, in a
filing today. The Isle of Man-based company said it won the
permits from the Karnataka State government.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Todd White at 
 twhite2@bloomberg.net  